snippet.title: CrossPlanet Closed Demo - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Join our Discord to get access later in the year: https://discord.gg/wRkCcNEYek

Arena shooter goes third person with CrossPlanet! A Free to play Sci Fi shooter with action packed Multiplayer. Our closed "Alpha Demo" is coming later this year for Windows PC! 

CrossPlanet on Twitter: https://twitter.com/CrossPlanetGame
CrossPlanet on Facebook: https://facebook.com/CrossPlanetGame
Our Gamejolt page: https://gamejolt.com/games/CrossPlanet/624055
